'''Shelagh Fraser''' ([[1920s#1920|1920]] &ndash; [[2000]])<ref name="Insider 52" /> was a British actress<ref name="Remembered" /> who was reportedly born either in Ireland<ref name="Insider 32" /> or in Surrey, England.<ref name="Insider 52" /> She played [[Luke Skywalker]]'s aunt, [[Beru Whitesun Lars]], in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']].<ref name="ANH">{{Film|IV}}</ref> For the role, she altered her accent.<ref name="Insider 32" /> Archive audio of her voice was used in ''[[Star Wars Rebels]]''.

